      "role": "user",
      "content": "but \"caring about myself\" just means dragging out this performance. if the whole system is just built on these empty expectations and forced productivity, then why am i even trying to fit into it? it feels like a lie. isn't there more to it than just pretending to be okay in a broken system?",
